properties.areaDesc: Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI; Green Bay south of line from  Oconto WI to Little Sturgeon Bay WI; Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 6 at 1:53AM CST until January 6 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt expected.

* WHERE...Green Bay south of line from Oconto WI to Little
Sturgeon Bay WI, Lake Michigan from Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers
WI and Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI.

* WHEN...Until noon CST today.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON CST TODAY... ...GALE WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 2 AM CST EARLY THIS MORNING
